{"type":null,"faqId":37120,"title":"白色TPU塑料腕带染色怎么办？B2商务版腕带掉漆、出现锈斑怎么办？B2腕带断裂怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、由于材料特性原因，如果您的手环是浅色TUP塑料腕带，请避免手环经常接触易掉色的深色衣物，防止染色</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、B2腕带或耳机掉漆、出现锈斑：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（1）您在使用的过程中是否沾过水？是否在水中浸泡？是否经常出汗？</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（2）腐蚀斑点问题研发已经分析，是因为接触了一些特殊液体混合物导致，例如质量较差的空气含有特别有害物质与汗液混合就容易腐蚀金属。建议用户在空气质量差的时候减少户外活动，手环尽量保持干燥，如果泡水建议尽快擦拭干。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、B2腕带断裂：按照流程上升CSE</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2284","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750143000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":314,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,腕带染色,塑料腕带,掉漆,断裂,染色","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}